OL,3,CThe bears helping people from across
OL,4,Cthe country deal with trauma
OL,6,FA woman from Merseyside has organised
OL,7,Fthe creation and delivery of thousands
OL,8,Fof knitted and crocheted "Trauma
OL,9,Fbears" to help vulnerable communities
OL,10,Facross the country deal with trauma.
OL,12,FJess Pearce, 64, from Wallasey in
OL,13,FMerseyside, made her first bear three
OL,14,Fyears ago since then she has set up a
OL,15,FFacebook group so others could join in.
