OL,3,CThe bears helping people from across
OL,4,Cthe country deal with trauma
OL,6,F"You could feel the deep sense of
OL,7,Fmourning for the whole area; it was
OL,8,Freally moving and then you felt the
OL,9,Fpositivity that the bears were going
OL,10,Fto bring," she added.
OL,12,FThe bears are made from wool, no two
OL,13,Fare the same and take several hours to
OL,14,Fmake.
OL,16,FThe 64-year-old said, "Every bear is
OL,17,Findividual, so when we've given them
OL,18,Fto three or four children, you can
OL,19,Ftell whose bear is whose, which is
OL,20,Flovely".
